WEBVTT

00:06.910 --> 00:11.120
ظآزIt makes no differenceظآز

00:16.170 --> 00:19.600
ظآزMaster, it's lateظآز

00:19.600 --> 00:23.530
ظآزWe must hurry on our journeyظآز

00:28.730 --> 00:32.370
ظآزI want to become a loyal officialظآز

00:32.370 --> 00:35.560
ظآزAt a time like thisظآز

00:36.050 --> 00:39.480
ظآزWhy are the scholarsظآز

00:39.480 --> 00:47.240
ظآزStill trying to be officials?ظآز

00:49.930 --> 00:50.770
I think

00:51.200 --> 00:53.520
it's the end of the road for you

00:53.750 --> 00:55.490
after being a loyal official
for so long.

00:57.840 --> 00:58.680
What do you think,

00:59.160 --> 01:00.240
Your Highness?

01:00.390 --> 01:03.950
(Crown Prince, Zhu Yousheng)

01:04.690 --> 01:07.570
In the past, my uncle, Duke of Ding,

01:07.770 --> 01:10.010
and all 237 people of the Jiang clan

01:10.010 --> 01:11.290
were framed.

01:12.650 --> 01:14.880
All 53,000 soldiers of the Ding Army

01:15.400 --> 01:16.680
were wronged and humiliated.

01:18.370 --> 01:21.247
Today, I wonder how many will it be
for the East Palace

01:21.800 --> 01:23.090
and the capital.

01:24.860 --> 01:26.490
You disregarded
your father, the emperor,

01:27.770 --> 01:29.850
and helped Zhu Youting seize the throne

01:30.570 --> 01:31.930
just to clear

01:32.880 --> 01:34.930
Ding Army's name.

01:36.400 --> 01:37.650
You are even putting the blame

01:38.730 --> 01:41.490
on Father and me.

01:43.130 --> 01:44.650
I will kill any suspect.

01:45.730 --> 01:48.290
(General of Cavalry, Song Mo)
You think you're wronged?

01:56.880 --> 01:57.770
Song Mo,

01:58.990 --> 02:00.680
I pity you.

02:01.190 --> 02:03.100
You took revenge on the wrong person.

02:04.770 --> 02:05.800
I lost.

02:07.570 --> 02:10.120
But you will also lose everything.

02:20.370 --> 02:21.960
- Your Highness!
- Your Highness!

02:25.610 --> 02:27.800
I'd rather die

02:28.400 --> 02:30.000
than obey a traitor.

02:57.720 --> 02:58.560
Sir,

02:58.650 --> 02:59.490
I found it.

03:00.890 --> 03:01.730
Congratulations, Sir.

03:01.960 --> 03:04.050
You're halfway to your revenge.

03:12.280 --> 03:13.210
He said

03:14.120 --> 03:15.800
I took revenge on the wrong person.

03:19.150 --> 03:21.460
(During the winter of the 27th year
of the Chengping era,)

03:21.960 --> 03:23.520
(while the emperor was gravely ill,)

03:23.960 --> 03:26.400
(General of Cavalry, Song Mo,
supported Lord Qing)

03:26.410 --> 03:28.120
(to launched a night attack
on the capital)

03:28.130 --> 03:29.970
(by using the excuse
of accompanying the emperor)

03:29.980 --> 03:32.060
(to avenge Duke of Ding
who suffered an injustice.)

03:41.500 --> 03:43.120
Having more than 100 weapons
is a felony.

03:43.120 --> 03:45.700
Did you know that Lord Qing
and Song Mo would start a rebellion?

03:45.960 --> 03:47.650
The capital is getting dangerous.

03:47.920 --> 03:49.880
The streets are filled
with rebels and refugees.

03:49.890 --> 03:51.030
(Marquis of Jining's Wife, Dou Zhao)
Who cares about a crime

03:51.050 --> 03:52.240
when in such a chaos?

03:52.530 --> 03:53.380
Take them.

03:53.400 --> 03:54.240
Yes!

04:03.090 --> 04:05.210
Song Mo is a cold-blooded killer.

04:05.720 --> 04:08.720
He murdered his father
and younger brother back then.

04:09.370 --> 04:11.840
Now, he has started a rebellion
and attacked the capital.

04:12.280 --> 04:13.650
Everyone is saying that Song Mo

04:14.210 --> 04:15.560
is going to wipe out the city.

04:15.560 --> 04:17.480
That was why I tried to escape.

04:17.750 --> 04:19.870
(Marquis of Jining, Wei Tingyu)
Ridiculous!

04:19.890 --> 04:20.960
How dare a servant like you

04:21.450 --> 04:23.330
gossip about
affairs of the imperial court?

04:23.770 --> 04:24.810
Beat him up!

04:26.360 --> 04:27.520
This traitor, Song Mo,

04:28.770 --> 04:29.890
is here to get revenge.

04:39.110 --> 04:42.390
(Shadow Guard, Chen Jia)

04:59.490 --> 05:01.410
(Court Eunuch of Ministry
of Imperial Ceremony, Wang Ge)

05:12.250 --> 05:13.480
After tonight,

05:13.810 --> 05:15.690
Lord Qing will become the emperor.

05:16.570 --> 05:18.400
General Song, you contributed the most.

05:19.478 --> 05:20.320
We are here

05:21.090 --> 05:22.280
to congratulate you.

05:22.920 --> 05:23.960
Do you know

05:24.600 --> 05:25.600
that what I did tonight

05:25.960 --> 05:27.920
was to avenge Duke of Ding?

05:29.090 --> 05:30.250
Once I meet His Majesty,

05:30.920 --> 05:33.010
I will hand this over to Lord Qing.

05:35.840 --> 05:37.400
His Majesty is having a conversation

05:37.400 --> 05:38.570
with His Highness.

05:38.570 --> 05:39.600
You shouldn't disturb him.

05:40.090 --> 05:41.400
When the throne changes hands,

05:42.250 --> 05:44.250
you will meet His Majesty.

05:45.210 --> 05:46.050
Fine.

05:49.010 --> 05:51.010
Ask him to come to me

05:51.210 --> 05:52.330
when he becomes the emperor.

05:53.520 --> 05:54.810
Everyone, heed my order!

05:55.330 --> 05:56.170
Yes!

05:56.810 --> 05:58.280
Move to the outskirts

05:59.840 --> 06:01.250
and await His Majesty's orders!

06:01.810 --> 06:02.650
Yes!

06:12.250 --> 06:14.070
(A new emperor
who couldn't ascend the throne)

06:14.100 --> 06:16.280
(and the rebels
who surround the capital's outskirts.)

06:17.040 --> 06:17.880
(An impasse.)

06:18.400 --> 06:19.250
(A chaos.)

06:20.290 --> 06:21.400
(Marquis of Jining's Residence)

06:21.400 --> 06:23.130
(At that time,
I would never have imagined)

06:24.095 --> 06:26.520
(that the seemingly stable residence)

06:27.330 --> 06:29.770
(already had
so many cracks within.)

06:31.010 --> 06:31.850
From tonight onwards,

06:32.570 --> 06:34.810
entertainment and repairs
in the residence are halted.

06:35.360 --> 06:37.070
The servants in charge,

06:37.300 --> 06:38.350
go purchase a month's worth

06:38.360 --> 06:40.400
of meat, vegetables,
and fruit tomorrow morning.

06:41.550 --> 06:43.570
Patrol the residence along this route.

06:43.890 --> 06:44.840
Rotate in four shifts.

06:45.260 --> 06:47.960
Assign blades and arrows
to the ten men at the entrances

06:47.970 --> 06:49.280
and have them guard there all day.

06:49.770 --> 06:51.000
Put two more men

06:51.160 --> 06:53.810
guard the duke, Ming,
and the three Madam's chambers.

06:54.280 --> 06:55.120
Yes.

06:55.250 --> 06:56.090
Madam.

06:57.270 --> 06:59.220
The duke and Lord Qing are relatives.

06:59.480 --> 07:01.090
(Ms. Tuo)
All the nobles

07:01.090 --> 07:01.940
and ministers

07:01.940 --> 07:04.130
are seeking an audience.

07:04.890 --> 07:05.810
At such a crucial time,

07:06.250 --> 07:08.160
Lord Qing's men
are calling for enthronement.

07:08.360 --> 07:10.440
(Dou Family's Second Daughter, Dou Ming)
The officials would risk themselves

07:10.450 --> 07:12.230
for the emperor.
There are fence sitters too.

07:12.770 --> 07:14.960
Everyone wants to drag Tingyu down.

07:18.130 --> 07:18.970
I'm not meeting them.

07:21.280 --> 07:22.600
But if I don't meet them,

07:23.440 --> 07:24.710
I might offend them.

07:25.960 --> 07:26.810
Carry it inside.

07:30.430 --> 07:32.910
(Libation)

07:35.890 --> 07:36.730
I am ill.

07:37.160 --> 07:38.210
I'm seriously ill.

07:38.810 --> 07:40.650
The duke is not meeting guests

07:41.250 --> 07:42.160
to take care of me.

07:42.690 --> 07:44.160
This is inappropriate.

07:44.480 --> 07:46.090
Can propriety help you overcome this?

07:46.920 --> 07:49.450
Nothing is greater than life and death.

07:50.360 --> 07:51.280
With the coffin here,

07:52.520 --> 07:53.520
you will have peace.

08:02.070 --> 08:05.430
(Libation)

09:44.990 --> 09:46.630
=Blossom=

09:46.631 --> 09:49.150
(Adapted from the novel
"Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

09:49.230 --> 09:52.190
=Episode 1=

09:54.930 --> 09:56.610
Buy 100 kilograms of charcoal.

09:56.810 --> 09:58.570
The duke and Ming like
to write and draw.

09:59.050 --> 10:00.600
Buy another 100 feet of paper.

10:00.840 --> 10:03.090
Ask all the managers
of estates and shops

10:03.720 --> 10:05.430
to come to see me after lunch.

10:05.840 --> 10:06.680
Yes.

10:07.690 --> 10:08.530
Madam.

10:10.090 --> 10:10.930
Here you go.

10:13.990 --> 10:15.380
Madam, the miscarriage

10:16.000 --> 10:17.330
almost killed you last year.

10:17.840 --> 10:19.240
The priority now

10:19.600 --> 10:20.960
is to take care of your health.

10:21.330 --> 10:22.810
Don't overwork.

10:27.140 --> 10:29.370
The wife of a big family
has to take care of everything.

10:30.600 --> 10:31.690
Serving my husband's family,

10:32.700 --> 10:34.790
taking care of his concubines,
illegitimate children,

10:35.300 --> 10:36.810
more than 100 people in the residence,

10:38.450 --> 10:40.360
and managing dozens

10:40.810 --> 10:41.810
of estates and shops.

10:42.840 --> 10:45.210
That's not counting
the usual social activities.

10:46.000 --> 10:47.170
The duke doesn't even ask you

10:47.960 --> 10:49.360
about your illness.

10:50.120 --> 10:51.550
Fifth Young Lady came from far away

10:52.240 --> 10:53.640
and said she'd take care of you

10:53.710 --> 10:54.930
but she was always not around.

10:55.930 --> 10:57.350
You're not from the same mother
after all.

10:57.360 --> 10:58.630
- She's so heartless.
- Ms. Tuo.

11:14.880 --> 11:15.720
Madam, look.

11:16.170 --> 11:17.410
It's not even spring yet

11:17.720 --> 11:19.450
but the Yulan magnolias are in bloom.

11:19.720 --> 11:22.810
It's my first time
seeing Yulan magnolias in the snow.

11:24.600 --> 11:25.740
My mother would be very happy

11:26.720 --> 11:27.720
if she could see it.

11:31.170 --> 11:32.760
If Seventh Madam were still around,

11:33.880 --> 11:36.570
you wouldn't have to work so hard.

11:45.640 --> 11:46.480
What's that smell?

11:48.690 --> 11:49.570
The smell of herbs.

11:51.930 --> 11:53.410
Someone's making herbal soup.

11:56.170 --> 11:57.810
It seems like Ming isn't slacking.

11:58.230 --> 11:59.410
She is making medicine for me.

11:59.930 --> 12:00.770
Yes.

12:01.210 --> 12:03.120
Don't talk about our mothers
in the future.

12:04.000 --> 12:05.970
Ming will feel sad if she hears it.

12:06.240 --> 12:07.080
Yes.

12:11.690 --> 12:13.050
I'm afraid the medicine is burnt.

12:23.050 --> 12:23.890
Don't worry.

12:24.210 --> 12:25.050
The physician said

12:25.240 --> 12:26.640
she would die soon.

12:27.000 --> 12:29.050
Once she dies and
the mourning period is over,

12:30.640 --> 12:31.690
I will marry you.

12:40.240 --> 12:41.330
He is right.

12:43.720 --> 12:45.450
Our marriage was decided by our parents.

12:46.090 --> 12:47.680
There were
never any feelings between us.

12:48.620 --> 12:50.090
If they have feelings for each other,

12:51.720 --> 12:52.840
he can marry Dou Ming

12:54.480 --> 12:55.600
after I die from illness,

12:57.090 --> 12:59.080
so the relationship
between the Wei and Dou family

12:59.840 --> 13:00.690
can be long-lasting.

13:00.960 --> 13:02.050
Madam.

13:03.330 --> 13:04.170
Let's go.

13:06.000 --> 13:07.290
I'm afraid Father won't allow it.

13:08.290 --> 13:09.720
Her mother and my mother

13:09.720 --> 13:10.860
were close friends back then.

13:11.570 --> 13:13.530
The relationship
between my mother and Father

13:13.530 --> 13:14.960
caused her mother's death.

13:17.760 --> 13:18.600
(Mother...)

13:19.530 --> 13:21.210
(Mother died because of her?)

13:27.210 --> 13:29.330
I've been doing my best
to manage the residence

13:30.410 --> 13:33.880
but ended up
helping my enemy instead.

13:35.810 --> 13:36.720
The kitchen is on fire.

13:37.760 --> 13:38.600
Get someone here.

13:38.720 --> 13:39.560
Yes.

13:41.240 --> 13:42.210
Don't worry.

13:42.810 --> 13:44.000
Don't you know me well?

13:45.290 --> 13:46.930
I will do everything I can

13:47.290 --> 13:48.360
to marry you.

13:49.090 --> 13:50.290
No one can separate us.

13:55.130 --> 13:56.110
There's a fire!

13:56.110 --> 13:57.530
- There's a fire!
- Hurry!

13:57.530 --> 13:59.050
- Hurry, there's a fire!
- Someone!

13:59.050 --> 13:59.890
What's that noise?

14:00.540 --> 14:01.580
- There's a fire!
- Hurry!

14:02.810 --> 14:03.650
Someone!

14:03.660 --> 14:04.640
Quick! There's a fire!

14:05.310 --> 14:06.720
- There's a fire!
- There's a fire!

14:06.720 --> 14:08.410
Hurry!

14:16.240 --> 14:17.080
Dear,

14:17.450 --> 14:18.290
it's my fault.

14:18.450 --> 14:19.330
Don't hurt Ming.

14:20.500 --> 14:21.530
I'm not going to harm her.

14:23.620 --> 14:24.840
But I want to thank both of you

14:26.360 --> 14:27.810
for not letting me remain clueless.

14:29.530 --> 14:31.240
- Sister.
- Don't call me that.

14:32.120 --> 14:34.050
I've never wanted love from you,

14:35.290 --> 14:36.480
or you.

14:37.330 --> 14:38.170
But both of you

14:38.840 --> 14:40.960
even trample on my last bit of feelings.

14:41.840 --> 14:43.410
How did my mother die?

14:47.210 --> 14:48.760
It was before I was born.

14:49.000 --> 14:50.720
But I heard the elders talk about it.

14:51.430 --> 14:52.810
I don't know so much.

14:54.330 --> 14:56.000
I will investigate this.

14:58.290 --> 14:59.830
However, there should be an explanation

15:00.810 --> 15:02.090
for what happens today.

15:05.600 --> 15:06.440
You...

15:12.240 --> 15:14.410
I, Dou Zhao, married into this family
for ten years

15:15.090 --> 15:16.480
and did my best every day

15:16.840 --> 15:18.050
to manage the residence.

15:19.410 --> 15:20.880
I've never let you, Wei Tingyu,

15:20.880 --> 15:21.840
or Dou Ming down.

15:23.300 --> 15:24.600
During the chaos of the capital,

15:25.270 --> 15:27.600
I've been looking after the residence
with my fragile body,

15:27.960 --> 15:28.810
but they

15:29.450 --> 15:31.120
were fornicating in the kitchen

15:31.120 --> 15:32.240
and cursing me to die.

15:34.120 --> 15:36.290
A heartless man cannot be relied on.

15:37.140 --> 15:39.240
The daughter of an enemy
cannot be a family of mine.

15:39.610 --> 15:42.080
When this scandal and grudge
is tried in court in the future,

15:42.330 --> 15:43.600
all of you are witnesses.

15:48.840 --> 15:49.720
From today onward,

15:50.280 --> 15:52.170
I'm no longer the wife
of the Marquis of Jining.

16:02.090 --> 16:02.930
Master!

16:04.360 --> 16:05.200
Master.

16:05.210 --> 16:06.410
Madam left in a carriage.

16:06.410 --> 16:07.250
Stupid.

16:07.400 --> 16:08.480
Don't you think I know that?

16:08.560 --> 16:10.280
I asked you to guard here.
What did you do?

16:10.290 --> 16:11.490
Why are you still spacing out?

16:11.500 --> 16:12.480
Get our clothes here.

16:13.100 --> 16:14.540
Yes!

16:18.200 --> 16:19.310
If I knew this would happen,

16:19.550 --> 16:20.790
I would've listened to my mother

16:21.390 --> 16:23.150
to put poison in her medicine

16:23.677 --> 16:24.997
to kill her.

16:27.750 --> 16:28.990
Why are you still here?

16:29.310 --> 16:30.550
If she goes to court,

16:30.680 --> 16:32.350
we won't live a peaceful life
from now on.

16:32.480 --> 16:33.320
Don't worry.

16:33.897 --> 16:35.317
She will never ruin the reputation

16:36.110 --> 16:37.590
of my family.

16:44.190 --> 16:48.550
Having talent and ambition

16:49.350 --> 16:53.990
without any place to show.

17:03.980 --> 17:04.820
Miss.

17:05.070 --> 17:06.310
It's snowing heavily.

17:16.390 --> 17:17.470
This isn't snow.

17:35.420 --> 17:36.260
Ms. Tuo,

17:36.390 --> 17:37.590
give them some food.

17:38.560 --> 17:39.400
Thank you.

17:39.950 --> 17:40.790
Thank you.

17:40.790 --> 17:43.710
(The land is ruined
and the empire will soon fall.)

17:44.390 --> 17:45.430
(Everything is unexpected.)

17:46.870 --> 17:48.510
(This ill-fated departure)

17:49.190 --> 17:50.270
(is my farewell.)

17:59.870 --> 18:01.190
The willow is born.

18:01.470 --> 18:02.710
Spin the top.

18:03.270 --> 18:04.310
The willow is green.

18:04.590 --> 18:05.830
Play the diabolo.

18:06.550 --> 18:07.790
The willow sprouts.

18:07.910 --> 18:08.750
Hit...

18:15.190 --> 18:16.030
Ms. Tuo.

18:17.430 --> 18:19.870
I was young when Mother passed away.

18:20.870 --> 18:23.630
Help me recall if there
was anything weird.

18:24.830 --> 18:28.290
The Old Master
just became a palace scholar.

18:28.820 --> 18:30.760
It was also your cousin's birthday.

18:31.190 --> 18:33.640
The late Madam asked me to bring you

18:33.790 --> 18:35.330
to tell your uncle this good news.

18:36.380 --> 18:38.380
When I came back,
the late Madam passed away.

18:39.160 --> 18:41.130
Later, Wang Yingxue
married into the family.

18:43.230 --> 18:44.070
Look out!

18:44.070 --> 18:44.910
Ms. Tuo!

19:21.830 --> 19:23.350
(A groundbreaking long spear)

19:24.030 --> 19:25.230
(and grey hair at a young age.)

19:25.990 --> 19:26.830
(Song Mo?)

19:27.750 --> 19:28.710
Miss, are you all right?

19:28.870 --> 19:29.710
Miss.

19:29.830 --> 19:30.670
Miss.

19:43.070 --> 19:43.910
Do you hear me?

19:44.790 --> 19:45.630
If you cry,

19:46.150 --> 19:48.150
I'll send you to the devil, Song Mo.

19:49.310 --> 19:50.350
He eats children.

19:52.710 --> 19:53.970
I'm not crying.

20:03.630 --> 20:04.470
Give me the rations.

20:07.350 --> 20:08.190
Go home.

20:15.310 --> 20:18.790
(He isn't
as cruel as the rumours suggest.)

20:19.750 --> 20:21.510
General, since you know the kids

20:21.510 --> 20:23.350
don't even dare to cry
when you're mentioned,

20:23.910 --> 20:25.790
(Ji Yong, Monk Name: Yuantong)
you should

20:25.790 --> 20:27.430
kill less in the future.

20:32.570 --> 20:34.430
It's a carriage
from Marquis of Jining's Residence.

20:34.430 --> 20:36.910
(Lu Ming)

20:38.710 --> 20:40.070
The capital is in chaos.

20:41.230 --> 20:42.590
Why do you come here?

20:45.230 --> 20:46.400
I'm going back to my hometown.

21:00.350 --> 21:03.150
You are so ill and you've gone
through an arduous journey.

21:03.870 --> 21:04.710
You can go to heaven

21:05.310 --> 21:06.390
instead of your hometown.

21:08.430 --> 21:09.870
Follow me to get warm at the temple.

21:10.910 --> 21:11.950
Have a bowl of herbal soup.

21:14.550 --> 21:15.390
Hold it.

21:15.710 --> 21:16.870
How can we accept

21:17.230 --> 21:19.350
(Lu Zheng)
an unknown person now?

21:19.710 --> 21:20.550
Lu Zheng.

21:39.800 --> 21:40.790
Everyone, hear my orders!

21:40.950 --> 21:41.790
Yes!

21:41.790 --> 21:43.290
Move to the back hill of Wanfo Temple!

21:43.310 --> 21:44.150
Yes!

21:47.990 --> 21:50.230
I thought it was an enemy scout.

21:50.510 --> 21:51.390
Sorry for what I did.

21:52.630 --> 21:53.470
Lu Ming.

21:55.030 --> 21:57.750
Fix the carriage
and escort her to the temple.

21:58.270 --> 21:59.110
Yes.

22:00.390 --> 22:01.230
Miss.

22:35.990 --> 22:36.830
I investigated it.

22:36.830 --> 22:38.580
There're only money and clothing
in the carriage.

22:50.590 --> 22:52.000
It's difficult to travel in the snow

22:52.270 --> 22:53.330
and you are very ill.

22:53.990 --> 22:55.490
Anything urgent?

22:57.790 --> 22:58.890
We shouldn't bother you

22:59.270 --> 23:01.190
with the family trifles, General.

23:01.190 --> 23:02.650
The general treated you with courtesy

23:03.150 --> 23:04.450
and allowed you to rest here.

23:04.930 --> 23:06.500
How dare you still hide things from us?

23:07.110 --> 23:07.990
Is this a trap?

23:07.990 --> 23:08.830
Lu Ming.

23:12.070 --> 23:12.910
Miss.

23:14.390 --> 23:15.530
You should know

23:16.030 --> 23:17.850
that everything will be decided
in a few days.

23:18.130 --> 23:20.650
Being cautious is the only way
to survive in a dangerous place.

23:23.270 --> 23:24.410
We must know everything.

23:26.610 --> 23:27.730
- General, I...
- Ms. Tuo.

23:31.630 --> 23:33.090
It's nothing important.

23:33.990 --> 23:35.410
It's just

23:36.110 --> 23:37.690
a family scandal, General.

23:38.950 --> 23:41.930
The Marquis of Jining
has been having an affair

23:42.750 --> 23:43.890
with my half-sibling

23:44.350 --> 23:45.410
while I am seriously ill.

23:46.190 --> 23:47.650
I witnessed it today

23:48.310 --> 23:49.730
and wanted to divorce immediately.

23:50.750 --> 23:53.370
However, the imperial court
had no one on duty

23:53.810 --> 23:54.890
due to the capital's chaos,

23:56.070 --> 23:57.090
so I had to

23:57.490 --> 23:59.580
return to my hometown
to report it to the officials.

24:01.710 --> 24:02.890
I see.

24:03.870 --> 24:04.710
I had

24:05.830 --> 24:06.850
offended you.

24:07.510 --> 24:08.810
You are too serious.

24:11.490 --> 24:13.490
I am no longer
the wife of the Marquis of Jining.

24:14.950 --> 24:15.890
My surname is Dou.

24:17.440 --> 24:18.810
I'm the fourth child of the family.

24:21.110 --> 24:23.610
A man's indulgence can be spoken of

24:24.070 --> 24:26.370
but a woman's indulgence cannot.

24:26.910 --> 24:28.090
Getting to know a person early

24:28.590 --> 24:29.810
and settle things quickly.

24:34.950 --> 24:36.330
Miss Dou,

24:36.750 --> 24:38.450
that's a blessing in disguise.

24:41.750 --> 24:43.370
General, you will rule the new empire.

24:44.150 --> 24:45.370
You have authority and power.

24:46.710 --> 24:48.330
Why do you have
a head full of grey hair?

24:49.190 --> 24:51.290
I can see dejection
in between your eyes.

24:56.070 --> 24:56.930
Sir.

25:00.550 --> 25:01.390
Sir.

25:08.270 --> 25:09.210
I'm sorry.

25:10.550 --> 25:11.890
A person who is dying

25:12.950 --> 25:14.330
gave his life to the wrong person.

25:18.790 --> 25:19.630
You are right.

25:20.870 --> 25:22.010
A person who is dying

25:24.030 --> 25:25.380
gave his life to the wrong person.

25:36.710 --> 25:37.850
The sun is coming up.

25:38.430 --> 25:41.170
Later, I'll have someone to escort you back
to your hometown.

25:42.190 --> 25:43.930
The sky looks weird today.

25:44.590 --> 25:46.190
The Fire Star enters
the Purple Forbidden Enclosure.

25:46.190 --> 25:47.250
It's a sign of chaos.

25:47.790 --> 25:49.690
However, the meteor is bright.

25:50.230 --> 25:51.390
The chaos of the capital

25:51.390 --> 25:53.250
is indeed the reflection,

25:53.510 --> 25:54.650
but the meteor...

26:00.730 --> 26:02.010
There should be a blessing
among the disasters.

26:02.500 --> 26:04.330
Both of you are fated.

26:06.350 --> 26:08.290
Master Yuantong, you overestimated me.

26:09.070 --> 26:11.210
A weak woman like me

26:11.990 --> 26:13.810
is just a passerby
who avoids the blizzard

26:14.430 --> 26:15.890
and gets a bowl of hot medicine.

26:16.910 --> 26:20.330
How will I be fated with General Song?

26:34.310 --> 26:35.150
What?

26:35.470 --> 26:37.930
Is Lord Qing not going
to give us an explanation?

26:41.390 --> 26:42.530
General Song!

26:42.870 --> 26:44.710
Even if you are almighty,

26:44.710 --> 26:46.130
if you do this,

26:46.510 --> 26:47.810
Lord Qing

26:48.150 --> 26:50.250
will still kill you.

26:51.070 --> 26:52.450
Whoever sits on the throne

26:52.950 --> 26:54.690
is cold-blooded.

26:54.950 --> 26:57.370
Duke of Ding sacrificed himself
to guard the border for 15 years

26:58.030 --> 26:59.870
but was accused of treason

26:59.870 --> 27:01.050
and was punished
with the annihilation of his clan.

27:01.340 --> 27:03.930
His Highness hasn't
ascended the throne yet

27:04.370 --> 27:06.930
and is already trying
to kill the one who helped him.

27:07.550 --> 27:09.980
Are you not worried
that the officials will be in fear?

27:13.310 --> 27:14.730
General Song, you're overthinking.

27:14.990 --> 27:15.950
If news goes out,

27:16.500 --> 27:18.750
it's just a scandal

27:18.750 --> 27:20.170
of Marquis of Jining's family.

27:20.470 --> 27:23.490
It has nothing to do with Lord Qing.

27:24.920 --> 27:26.990
Am I right?

27:32.310 --> 27:34.290
(Granted by the Emperor)
By Lord Qing's edict,

27:35.230 --> 27:37.670
Song Mo became arrogant.

27:37.671 --> 27:38.890
He abused favour
and acted against reason

27:39.270 --> 27:40.330
to kidnap

27:40.750 --> 27:43.150
and eloped with
Marquis of Jining's wife, Dou Zhao.

27:43.330 --> 27:44.860
Wei Tingyu, you...

27:44.870 --> 27:47.230
With both of them captured together,
they will be executed

27:47.230 --> 27:48.090
as the family's law.

27:50.430 --> 27:52.010
Putting the blame on a woman.

27:52.550 --> 27:55.290
Lord Qing is more shameless
than his father, the previous emperor.

27:55.750 --> 27:56.730
General Song,

27:57.430 --> 28:00.150
if you hand over the jade seal

28:00.150 --> 28:01.410
and commit suicide,

28:01.670 --> 28:06.050
Lord Qing will leave your body whole.

28:06.390 --> 28:07.250
Unfortunately,

28:07.830 --> 28:08.970
I'm very petty.

28:09.550 --> 28:11.370
I won't leave both your bodies whole.

28:20.470 --> 28:25.650
Kill!

28:32.310 --> 28:33.150
Madam,

28:33.510 --> 28:34.930
please come with me
to hide at the back hill.

28:35.470 --> 28:37.050
Let's go.

28:40.310 --> 28:42.010
When Lord Qing stopped me
from meeting His Majesty,

28:42.590 --> 28:44.450
I knew he was going to betray me.

28:44.590 --> 28:46.330
- Sir.
- I gave him a chance.

28:46.750 --> 28:48.330
If he kept his promise to meet me,

28:49.150 --> 28:50.730
I would spare him.

28:51.430 --> 28:53.890
However, he went
to Xishanxing Palace instead.

28:53.890 --> 28:55.230
(Xishanxing Palace)

28:55.230 --> 28:56.530
The elites of the Ding Army I deployed

28:57.070 --> 28:59.810
did not go to waste.

29:00.750 --> 29:02.970
How does killing me benefit Song Mo?

29:03.310 --> 29:04.950
Even if he wants to rule the kingdom,

29:04.950 --> 29:06.310
I can grant him the opportunity.

29:06.310 --> 29:07.670
(Lord Qing, Zhu Youting)
Kill!

29:07.670 --> 29:09.930
Kill!

29:11.790 --> 29:13.010
Lord Qing

29:13.670 --> 29:15.530
is supposed to be dead by now.

29:20.230 --> 29:21.970
You're just bluffing.

29:22.990 --> 29:23.830
Take him down.

29:28.830 --> 29:30.250
Sir.

29:32.430 --> 29:34.590
(Qiguang Wanfo Pagoda)

29:38.630 --> 29:40.910
Get ready for battle!

29:40.910 --> 29:43.530
Kill!

29:48.270 --> 29:49.110
Miss.

29:51.190 --> 29:52.030
Be careful.

30:22.270 --> 30:23.780
Ding Army is brave and excels in battle.

30:23.790 --> 30:25.190
We have been surrounded now.

30:25.190 --> 30:26.710
What should we do?

30:26.710 --> 30:28.850
Don't worry. If your wife is dead,

30:29.630 --> 30:31.110
Song Mo is just a criminal general

30:31.110 --> 30:32.530
no matter how powerful he is.

30:34.990 --> 30:35.830
Sir!

31:36.270 --> 31:38.250
Miss, go quickly!

31:46.990 --> 31:48.170
I'll kill you!

31:51.990 --> 31:53.150
How can

31:53.150 --> 31:55.090
a weak woman like you

31:55.670 --> 31:56.890
kill anyone?

32:17.510 --> 32:18.350
Ms. Tuo!

33:11.310 --> 33:12.150
General.

33:16.470 --> 33:17.310
General.

33:17.510 --> 33:19.210
I didn't know about Wei Tingyu's plans.

33:23.190 --> 33:24.490
I'm seriously poisoned

33:25.270 --> 33:26.490
and going to die soon.

33:27.430 --> 33:28.570
I'm just sorry

33:29.110 --> 33:31.130
I can't avenge the Duke of Ding.

33:31.790 --> 33:33.130
But I caused you

33:33.630 --> 33:36.010
to get your name tarnished
and your life in danger.

33:36.710 --> 33:38.050
You saved me

33:39.150 --> 33:40.810
last night at the outskirts.

33:44.230 --> 33:45.730
I got you into this.

33:47.310 --> 33:49.090
Let's go. I'll take you away.

33:58.910 --> 33:59.750
Yuantong.

33:59.990 --> 34:00.970
Master Yuantong.

34:02.510 --> 34:03.350
Yuantong.

34:21.430 --> 34:24.070
(Records of the Enlightened Age)

34:24.070 --> 34:24.910
Go.

34:26.310 --> 34:27.150
Go.

34:27.670 --> 34:29.070
- Over there.
- Let's leave together.

34:29.070 --> 34:29.970
I'm not important.

34:30.230 --> 34:32.610
A blessing in disguise.
Both of you are fated.

34:33.110 --> 34:34.730
Both of you can change destiny.

34:35.510 --> 34:37.490
Go.

34:37.910 --> 34:38.790
They are over there!

34:38.790 --> 34:39.630
Catch them!

34:39.870 --> 34:40.710
Hurry!

35:09.630 --> 35:10.470
Look out!

35:49.070 --> 35:51.450
(Don't be a woman.)

35:53.010 --> 35:56.130
(Your happiness will
be in others' hands.)

35:59.590 --> 36:02.410
(Not only married couples
in the mortal realm will change.)

36:04.310 --> 36:07.010
(It's also the same for
an emperor and his officials.)

36:09.790 --> 36:11.010
(Being grateful in dawn)

36:13.030 --> 36:14.370
(and killing them at dusk.)

36:25.470 --> 36:27.470
(Records of the Enlightened Age)

36:30.590 --> 36:31.770
(I've never had)

36:33.110 --> 36:34.890
(a moment in my life)

36:34.890 --> 36:36.350
(Records of the Enlightened Age)

36:36.350 --> 36:38.050
(where I have a choice.)

37:37.270 --> 37:38.110
You're finally awake.

37:38.470 --> 37:39.830
You were entranced while reading

37:39.830 --> 37:41.250
and hit yourself in the mirror.

37:57.630 --> 37:58.470
This...

37:59.230 --> 38:00.070
What?

38:00.950 --> 38:01.850
Ms. Longevity.

38:03.310 --> 38:04.150
Miss!

38:05.550 --> 38:06.390
Ms. Longevity.

38:06.390 --> 38:07.230
Miss.

38:07.910 --> 38:10.350
(Dou Family's Mistress, Zhao Guqiu)
You're awake.

38:22.870 --> 38:23.850
Mother.

38:28.350 --> 38:29.290
Ms. Tuo.

38:36.630 --> 38:37.850
You are here.

38:45.790 --> 38:47.730
Why are you being coquettish?

38:53.590 --> 38:54.690
It's all my fault.

38:55.870 --> 38:58.230
Madam begged Buddha to bless Master

38:58.230 --> 38:59.650
into becoming a scholar.

39:00.270 --> 39:02.050
I also went to make a wish.

39:02.390 --> 39:04.050
I didn't look after you.

39:04.670 --> 39:06.570
Become a scholar?

39:07.610 --> 39:08.870
Is this

39:08.870 --> 39:10.090
the eighth year of the Chengping era?

39:12.430 --> 39:13.270
Yes.

39:15.510 --> 39:18.210
But I've lived my life.

39:19.110 --> 39:20.050
Just now,

39:20.910 --> 39:22.930
the temple was full of Shadow Guards.

39:23.950 --> 39:25.490
I died in front of the mirror.

39:27.630 --> 39:28.530
Miss.

39:29.710 --> 39:32.090
Zhuang Zhou dreams of the butterfly.
The butterfly dreams of Zhuang Zhou.

39:32.510 --> 39:33.490
It's just a dream.

39:34.350 --> 39:37.170
You read a storybook
until you were too immersed.

39:37.310 --> 39:39.170
You hit your head
and had a crazy dream.

39:39.472 --> 39:41.370
The dream and you are two things.

39:43.230 --> 39:45.830
(Records of the Enlightened Age)

39:46.110 --> 39:47.850
Records of the Enlightened Age?

39:48.710 --> 39:51.070
It was a storybook left by a hermit

39:51.070 --> 39:52.610
for a fated person.

39:54.310 --> 39:55.190
I think

39:55.190 --> 39:57.090
you are the Little Zhuang Zhou
who is fated to it.

39:57.210 --> 39:58.970
Thank you, Master Yuantong.

40:01.070 --> 40:02.410
Are you Yuantong?

40:13.350 --> 40:14.190
Mo!

40:17.830 --> 40:18.930
You are finally awake.

40:20.430 --> 40:21.270
Mo!

40:21.950 --> 40:23.890
I was so scared because you had
a nightmare and couldn't wake up.

40:24.470 --> 40:26.450
Thankfully, the abbot treated you.

40:27.270 --> 40:29.690
(Duke of Ying's Wife, Jiang Huisun)
How are you? Feeling better?

40:31.070 --> 40:32.250
Mother.

40:32.590 --> 40:35.090
I had a very long dream.

40:36.280 --> 40:38.310
However, I forgot everything

40:38.650 --> 40:39.970
about the dream.

40:40.950 --> 40:42.250
That's good.

40:42.830 --> 40:44.210
Everything in life

40:44.670 --> 40:46.770
has the wisdom
and virtuous appearance of Buddha.

40:47.110 --> 40:49.170
But due to delusion and attachment,

40:50.110 --> 40:51.370
they cannot attain realization.

40:52.030 --> 40:53.050
Thank you, Abbott.

40:54.430 --> 40:55.930
However, I think

40:57.470 --> 40:58.610
I shouldn't forget the dream.

41:04.790 --> 41:07.330
(On the day of becoming a scholar,)

41:07.950 --> 41:10.330
(a man complains)
(The Yulan magnolia wilts.)

41:11.070 --> 41:13.850
(Records of the Enlightened Age)
(ambition goes away with the wind.)

41:14.470 --> 41:17.290
(Focusing on the bad times and
regret not cherishing the good times.)

41:18.350 --> 41:19.610
(Why does it feel like a defeat)

41:20.110 --> 41:21.850
(after becoming a scholar?)

41:43.350 --> 41:44.190
Ms. Longevity?

41:46.870 --> 41:47.710
What are you looking at?

41:49.910 --> 41:51.610
Is this storybook so nice?

41:53.070 --> 41:53.910
He succeeded.

41:55.270 --> 41:56.110
He succeeded?

41:56.720 --> 41:57.560
Madam!

41:58.450 --> 41:59.290
Madam!

41:59.990 --> 42:01.290
He succeeded!

42:03.230 --> 42:04.230
Master did it.

42:04.230 --> 42:05.090
Seventh rank on the second tier.

42:07.470 --> 42:08.490
That's great.

42:09.030 --> 42:10.630
Shiying finally gets his wish

42:10.630 --> 42:12.050
after studying day and night.

42:14.390 --> 42:15.530
Who did you hear from

42:15.830 --> 42:17.290
about your father's success?

42:18.270 --> 42:19.110
I...

42:19.150 --> 42:21.250
This temple is a good place.

42:21.620 --> 42:22.470
Madam

42:22.470 --> 42:24.270
also came to pray for Wang Yingxue's

42:24.270 --> 42:25.110
family matters.

42:25.110 --> 42:26.330
- Wang Yingxue?
- Everything has come true.

42:29.430 --> 42:30.970
(Father studied hard for many years)

42:31.550 --> 42:33.250
(and finally
became a scholar that year.)

42:34.470 --> 42:35.850
(While the whole family
was celebrating,)

42:36.670 --> 42:37.910
(Mother fell ill suddenly.)

42:37.910 --> 42:38.750
Mother!

42:38.950 --> 42:39.970
What's wrong, Mother?

42:40.470 --> 42:41.610
(After Mother passed away,)

42:42.190 --> 42:43.530
(Wang Yingxue married into the family)

42:44.430 --> 42:45.430
(and became my stepmother.)

42:45.430 --> 42:46.710
Her mother and my mother

42:46.710 --> 42:48.090
were close friends back then.

42:48.670 --> 42:50.690
The relationship
between my mother and Father

42:50.950 --> 42:52.370
caused her mother's death.

42:53.670 --> 42:54.510
Gao Sheng.

42:54.510 --> 42:55.370
Prepare the carriage.

42:55.830 --> 42:56.690
Yes, Madam.

42:57.750 --> 42:59.350
Ms. Tuo, take her to Zhao Residence

42:59.350 --> 43:01.350
to tell my brother the good news.

43:01.350 --> 43:02.580
It's Zhangru's birthday as well.

43:02.580 --> 43:03.420
- No.
- Yes.

43:05.430 --> 43:07.370
I haven't seen Father for a long time.

43:07.710 --> 43:10.190
Why not invite Uncle and my cousin

43:10.190 --> 43:11.130
to celebrate together?

43:11.310 --> 43:12.510
Uncle is a vice censor-in-chief.

43:12.510 --> 43:14.130
He has the power
to impeach other officials.

43:14.310 --> 43:15.950
His reports
can be presented to His Majesty.

43:15.950 --> 43:17.230
It will be good for Father

43:17.380 --> 43:18.250
when he becomes an official.

43:20.950 --> 43:23.930
How do you know all these?

43:25.910 --> 43:26.770
That's a good thing.

43:26.950 --> 43:29.670
I haven't reunited
with Brother for a long time.

43:29.670 --> 43:31.210
Go and invite my brother.

43:32.190 --> 43:33.390
We can finally taste

43:33.390 --> 43:35.970
the jar of wine I buried for Shiying

43:36.230 --> 43:37.450
when I married into the family.

43:38.070 --> 43:39.330
I must thank Buddha for the blessing.

43:39.710 --> 43:41.090
Give it to me.

43:42.400 --> 43:43.240
Slow down.

43:45.200 --> 43:46.040
Ms. Tuo,

43:46.270 --> 43:47.410
Father went to the capital
for the imperial exam.

43:47.550 --> 43:49.170
Does Wang Yingxue live
in the capital too?

43:49.670 --> 43:50.510
Yes.

43:50.830 --> 43:52.890
Miss Wang's father was demoted

43:53.030 --> 43:53.970
and her family was in decline.

43:54.350 --> 43:56.650
They sold cotton and rice
for a living in Chanxi.

43:57.350 --> 43:58.990
When Master studied in Chanxi,

43:58.990 --> 44:00.170
Madam asked Master

44:00.170 --> 44:02.170
to bring some money to Miss Wang.

44:04.630 --> 44:06.090
Ask Uncle to come immediately.

44:06.350 --> 44:07.190
The sooner, the better.

44:08.910 --> 44:09.750
Yes.

44:17.750 --> 44:19.450
(What has happened cannot be rectified,)

44:20.150 --> 44:21.850
(but I can still change the future.)

44:23.070 --> 44:24.130
(Since the Records
of the Enlightened Age)

44:24.750 --> 44:26.610
(has fate recorded in it,)

44:27.910 --> 44:29.050
(I can change its ending)

44:30.310 --> 44:31.450
(since I've known it)

44:31.990 --> 44:33.650
(while it is in my hands.)

44:36.110 --> 44:36.950
(Mother,)

44:37.470 --> 44:38.610
(no matter how hard
and dangerous it is,)

44:39.190 --> 44:40.370
(I will protect you)

44:41.430 --> 44:43.250
(from anyone.)

45:01.190 --> 45:03.110
Dou Shiying went away to study,

45:03.110 --> 45:04.370
but he was cheating.

45:04.510 --> 45:06.110
If you dare force my sister,

45:06.110 --> 45:08.110
I, Zhao Si, will kill you

45:08.110 --> 45:10.590
even if I have to sacrifice my life!

45:10.590 --> 45:12.370
If you can't forgive me,

45:12.630 --> 45:14.570
just grant me a white cloth
to commit suicide.

45:14.710 --> 45:15.970
If you want to die so badly,

45:16.430 --> 45:17.270
take it.

45:18.630 --> 45:20.790
ظآزQuiet as serene wavesظآز

45:21.030 --> 45:24.490
ظآزI'm aware of
the vast and turbulent worldظآز

45:24.945 --> 45:29.040
ظآزMoving forward alone, the expectations
of many are hard to bearظآز

45:29.520 --> 45:33.270
ظآزWhen the time comes,
I will cast aside a lifetime of prideظآز

45:33.450 --> 45:36.180
ظآزTo wear a flower stick for youظآز

45:36.430 --> 45:38.640
ظآزOr perhaps my heart
yearns for the other sideظآز

45:38.640 --> 45:40.900
ظآزYet there's no place
for me to go in the endظآز

45:41.250 --> 45:44.520
ظآزYour presence by my side
is irreplaceableظآز

45:44.933 --> 45:48.133
ظآزLike a ship
crossing the desolate riverظآز

45:48.410 --> 45:52.250
ظآزThat brings me
through a chapter of my lifeظآز

45:52.390 --> 45:56.120
ظآزYou are the light
that saves me in the darknessظآز

45:56.860 --> 46:00.020
ظآزHaving you is a blessingظآز

46:00.480 --> 46:02.360
ظآزMy heart filled with warmthظآز

46:02.680 --> 46:06.210
ظآزBy your side,
I spend the rest of my lifeظآز

46:06.840 --> 46:09.680
ظآزYour presence by my side
is irreplaceableظآز

46:10.520 --> 46:13.630
ظآزWhere my heart yearns
is where I will goظآز

46:14.370 --> 46:17.610
ظآزBreaking waves over the desolate riverظآز

46:18.029 --> 46:21.699
ظآزThe wind rises as my heart finds peaceظآز

46:21.780 --> 46:25.820
ظآزYou are the light
that saves me in the darknessظآز

46:26.180 --> 46:29.660
ظآزHaving you is a blessingظآز

46:29.910 --> 46:33.190
ظآزOnly by being by your sideظآز

46:33.390 --> 46:37.770
ظآزI can spend the rest of my lifeظآز

46:38.100 --> 46:41.560
